# Web admin API base. Empty = same-origin relative URLs (the backend serves the
# built SPA, and the Vite dev server proxies /v1 → http://localhost:8080).
#
# Environments:
#   local       npm run dev            → empty base, dev proxy → http://localhost:8080
#   staging     npm run build:staging  → .env.staging  (your private pre-prod host)
#   production  npm run build:prod     → .env.prod      (bibotracker.com)
#
# Override ad-hoc by exporting VITE_API_BASE before a build.
VITE_API_BASE=
